{"3611010": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Ballad of Bullets", "steam_appid": 3611010, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/ac037efa9031358407ff168741eb6df3.webp?t=1775836968\" width=279 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   Rowell City is waiting for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   Add Ballad of Bullets to your Steam Wishlist and be the first to experience its dark descent on release day.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/f9ea6d6cdecb0657248280d067280558.webp?t=1775836968\" width=207 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   Ballad of Bullets is a story-driven, open-world 2D turn-based RPG inspired by the American crime cinema of the 1980s.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   With its adult themes, character-focused writing, and retro-noir aesthetic, the game doesn’t just lead the player through an adventure — it drags them into a slow-burning collapse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   Packed with rich dialogue, strategic combat, a world that changes over time, and unforgettable characters, Ballad of Bullets offers a dark and daring alternative for fans of classic RPGs</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/873db1fd902a385ba43803d34485e1f5.webp?t=1775836968\" width=176 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   The middle child of the Russell family is a young man abandoned by the military and haunted by his past.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   His father's sudden death brings him back to Rowell City after years — but this return is about more than a funeral.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  The shadows of his past, an alcoholic brother, a missing sister, and his father’s former criminal ties are all waiting to pull him into a darker destiny.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   In a city woven with crime, passion, and betrayal, his choices will shape not only his future — but the fate of his soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>And for some things, it’s already too late.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/b8ddcace127811416b13a0ba191778a8.poster.avif?t=1775836968\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/b8ddcace127811416b13a0ba191778a8.webm?t=1775836968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/b8ddcace127811416b13a0ba191778a8.mp4?t=1775836968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/817a60eea6b30fe6d48748ac0a3f4bb8.webp?t=1775836968\" width=323 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   Ballad of Bullets is not just about bloodshed and bullets — it's about the dangerous liaisons that bloom in the shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   From love affairs to desperate alliances, Rowell City is a place where intimacy and betrayal walk hand in hand.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/d2bd78188d4239884fd2f40488f8b077.poster.avif?t=1775836968\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/d2bd78188d4239884fd2f40488f8b077.webm?t=1775836968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/d2bd78188d4239884fd2f40488f8b077.mp4?t=1775836968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   Players will navigate complex relationships, indulge in moments of lust and tenderness, and uncover secrets that threaten to destroy everything they know.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/d73c57a17bf177a476e5b4a4906ed087.poster.avif?t=1775836968\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/d73c57a17bf177a476e5b4a4906ed087.webm?t=1775836968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/d73c57a17bf177a476e5b4a4906ed087.mp4?t=1775836968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Desire is never innocent — and in this city, every touch may come with a price.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/afe21d0b08caf98688790a586ff3be2b.webp?t=1775836968\" width=279 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/151348325ab02cda5431ec536a6fb432.poster.avif?t=1775836968\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/151348325ab02cda5431ec536a6fb432.webm?t=1775836968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/151348325ab02cda5431ec536a6fb432.mp4?t=1775836968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/8a41925a70d979e35048db45948220e3.poster.avif?t=1775836968\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/8a41925a70d979e35048db45948220e3.webm?t=1775836968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/8a41925a70d979e35048db45948220e3.mp4?t=1775836968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Open World RPG</strong>:</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore distinct districts, interact with NPCs, uncover hidden quests and buried secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Turn-Based Tactical Combat:</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic turn-based system enriched with weapon-specific abilities, status effects, and strategic depth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/f76f585fb1c4d859197106ffbd44a9b7.poster.avif?t=1775836968\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/f76f585fb1c4d859197106ffbd44a9b7.webm?t=1775836968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/f76f585fb1c4d859197106ffbd44a9b7.mp4?t=1775836968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deep Narrative Design:</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Adult themes, dramatic character arcs, and a branching storyline.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Time &amp; Weather System:</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic day/night cycles and evolving weather influence both the city and its inhabitants.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>1980s Aesthetic:</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A visual style that captures the spirit of the era with old-school pixel art and analog textures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/eb42c25874ba876547b32ffd02f25023.webp?t=1775836968\" width=323 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   Ballad of Bullets contains mature content including violence, sexual themes, substance use, and strong language.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It is intended for players 18 years and older.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   Any discriminatory, sexist, or racist content within the game world is purely fictional and does not reflect the views of the developers.</p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3611010/extras/ac037efa9031358407ff168741eb6df3.webp?t=1775836968\" width=279 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   Rowel